data.actual_result: You'll get a loading screen after jumping and a nelly crash when you try to click on a channel
data.expected_result: You should be able to jump to the message as normal and click on other channel's normally
data.short_description: Discord crashes when clicking a channel you search for something in
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to any server - Go to the search option and search anything, for example rick - Attempt to jump to any of the results - After jumping you'll get a screen similar to what you get when you're in a server when you leave it - Click on any channel in the server you searched in, you'll the the nelly crash
